Squizzy:;

She slowly started to wake up.  She heard the sounds of lazar fire 
and shells exploding.  She was still groggy, but coming around.  She 
then saw that she was still in the hands of a huge bot.  She looked 
around and saw the fight around her.  She screamed at the bot who was 
holding her. "LET ME GO!"
